<h1>Joining the SCL</h1>
        <p>The SCL is open to anyone who has an interest in the classics and is of college age or above. The $6 membership fee is good for the first four years following high school graduation; this period is called Primary Membership. After that, you can pay an additional $4 for four more years of SCL membership, called Secondary membership.</p>
		<p>If you have any questions about membership, you can contact the <%=link_to "NSCL Treasurer", :controller => "business/officers", :link => "treasurer" %> for further information.</p>
		<p>If you are interested, just fill out this handy form.</p>
		
		<%= form_tag :action => 'submit_application' %>
		<label for="member_first">First Name:</label><%= text_field 'member', 'first' %><br />
		<label for="member_last">Last Name:</label><%= text_field 'member', 'last' %><br />
		<label for="member_email">E-mail:</label><%= text_field 'member', 'email' %><br />
		<label for="member_phone">Phone Number:</label><%= text_field 'member', 'phone' %><br />
		<label for="member_grad_year">Year of HS Graduation:</label><%= text_field 'member', 'grad_year', { :size => '4', :maxlength => '4' } %><br />
<!--
		<h2>Home Address</h2>
		
